[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……この辺りも、鉱石は見当たらない。\nもう少し奥まで行くしかないか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "岩の割れ目とか、見落としがちな場所も見てみよ！\n案外こういう所に見つかったりするんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……分かった、ありがとう。\n姉さんも、手伝ってくれる？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ、もちろん。お宝探しなら\nトレジャーハンターの得意とするところよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "お？　それなら発掘屋だって負けないよ？\n一攫千金、狙うしかないね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "そういえば、前にレスナちゃんたちとも\nここで「ハイネの炎石」っていう石探しをしたんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、依頼のために頑張ってたなぁ……\n今は「果ての大陸」を探して海に出てるんだってね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ。仲間たちと一緒に頑張ってるみたい。\n最近は、顔つきも立派に変わった気がするわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "うん。今も夢を追いかけてるって聞くと、\nこっちまで嬉しくなるよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "ユリエさんは、夢ってある？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "私？　私は……本を書くこと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "いずれ、この世界でも元の世界でも、\nもっと色んな場所に行って、見たものを綴りたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "へえ、素敵じゃない。\nもう夢に向かって歩き始めてるんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ありがとう。\nまだ道半ばだけど、歩みは止めないつもり",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "ミルカちゃんも、夢はある？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……今は、目的の鉱石を探すことで精一杯",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "それも立派な夢だよ。わたしもやりたいことは\nあるけど、日々の仕事も大事だしね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "さーて、鉱石探しに戻ろうか。\nあの岩の奥、まだ見てない場所がありそう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そうね。ミルカ、行ってみましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……うん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]